#: ../../source/index.rst:2
msgid "TensorCircuit Next Generation"
msgstr "TensorCircuit Next Generation"

#: ../../source/index.rst:8
msgid ""
"**Welcome and congratulations! You have found TensorCircuit: the Next "
"Generation.** 👏"
msgstr "**欢迎并祝贺你！你发现了 TensorCircuit-NG。** 👏"

#: ../../source/index.rst:12
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "介绍"

#: ../../source/index.rst:14
msgid ""
"`TensorCircuit-NG <https://github.com/tensorcircuit/tensorcircuit-ng>`_ "
"is an industrial-grade, open-source high-performance quantum software "
"framework in Python. It is designed for researchers and engineers who "
"demand **Speed, Flexibility, and Elegance**."
msgstr ""
"`TensorCircuit-NG <https://github.com/tensorcircuit/tensorcircuit-ng>`_ "
"是一个工业级、开源的高性能 Python 量子软件框架。它专为追求 **速度、灵活性和优雅** 的研究人员和工程师而设计。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:20
msgid "🧬 Built for Humans"
msgstr "🧬 为人类而生"

#: ../../source/index.rst:23
msgid ""
"Intuitive API that feels like natural quantum physics. Focus on your "
"research, not the boilerplate."
msgstr "直观的 API，感受自然的量子物理。专注于你的研究，而非繁琐的代码。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:25
msgid "🚀 Extreme Performance"
msgstr "🚀 极致性能"

#: ../../source/index.rst:28
msgid ""
"Achieve **10-100x GPU speedup**. Powered by JIT compilation and optimized"
" tensor engines."
msgstr "实现 **10-100 倍 GPU 加速**。由 JIT 编译和优化的张量引擎驱动。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:30
msgid "🤖 Deep ML Fusion"
msgstr "🤖 深度机器学习融合"

#: ../../source/index.rst:33
msgid ""
"Native integration with **JAX, TensorFlow, and PyTorch**. Seamlessly "
"combine AD with quantum kernels."
msgstr "原生集成 **JAX、TensorFlow 和 PyTorch**。将自动微分与量子核无缝结合。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:35
msgid "⛓️ Advanced Engines"
msgstr "⛓️ 先进引擎"

#: ../../source/index.rst:38
msgid ""
"State-of-the-art support for **Noisy, Analog, Approximate and "
"Stabilizer** simulations."
msgstr "为 **含噪、模拟、近似和稳定器** 模拟提供最先进的支持。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:40
msgid "☁️ Hardware Agnostic"
msgstr "☁️ 硬件无关"

#: ../../source/index.rst:43
msgid ""
"Run your code anywhere: from local CPUs to distributed GPUs/TPUs and "
"**QPU providers** via a unified interface."
msgstr "随处运行你的代码：从本地 CPU 到分布式 GPU/TPU，以及通过统一接口访问的 **量子硬件（QPU）提供商**。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:45
msgid "🛠 Industrial Strength"
msgstr "🛠 工业级强度"

#: ../../source/index.rst:48
msgid ""
"Committed to stability and performance. **Long-term support** and proven "
"by extensive research and industrial applications."
msgstr "致力于稳定性和性能。**长期支持**，并经过广泛的研究和工业应用验证。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:52
msgid ""
"Please cite our published `whitepaper <https://quantum-"
"journal.org/papers/q-2023-02-02-912/>`_ when using TensorCircuit or "
"TensorCircuit-NG in your research. The bibtex information is provided by "
"``tc.cite()``."
msgstr ""
"在研究中使用 TensorCircuit 或 TensorCircuit-NG 时，请引用我们已发表的`白皮书 <https://quantum-journal.org/papers/q-2023-02-02-912/>`_。BibTeX 信息可通过 ``tc.cite()`` 获取。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:55
msgid ""
"TensorCircuit-NG is the active continuation of TensorCircuit project. We "
"recommend upgrading to TensorCircuit-NG for the latest features and "
"improvements. You can upgrade by running the following command: ``pip "
"uninstall tensorcircuit && pip install tensorcircuit-ng``"
msgstr ""
"TensorCircuit-NG 是 TensorCircuit 项目的活跃延续。我们建议升级到 TensorCircuit-NG 以获取最新功能和改进。您可以通过运行以下命令进行升级：``pip uninstall tensorcircuit && pip install tensorcircuit-ng``"

