"TensorCircuit is created and now maintained as `TensorCircuit-NG "
"<https://github.com/tensorcircuit/tensorcircuit-ng>`_ by `Shi-Xin Zhang "
"<https://github.com/refraction-ray>`_."
msgstr "TensorCircuit 由 `Shi-Xin Zhang <https://github.com/refraction-ray>`_ 创建，现作为 `TensorCircuit-NG <https://github.com/tensorcircuit/tensorcircuit-ng>`_ 维护。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:94
msgid ""
"The current core authors of TensorCircuit-NG are `Shi-Xin Zhang "
"<https://github.com/refraction-ray>`_ and `Yu-Qin Chen "
"<https://github.com/yutuer21>`_. We also thank `contributions "
"<https://github.com/tensorcircuit/tensorcircuit-ng/graphs/contributors>`_"
" from the open source community."
msgstr "TensorCircuit-NG 目前的核心作者是 `Shi-Xin Zhang <https://github.com/refraction-ray>`_ 和 `Yu-Qin Chen <https://github.com/yutuer21>`_。我们也感谢来自开源社区的`贡献 <https://github.com/tensorcircuit/tensorcircuit-ng/graphs/contributors>`_。"

